The Persistent Organic Pollutants Review Committee
 1. Takes note of the information provided to the Committee on the global monitoring plan for newly listed persistent organic pollutants;
 2. Acknowledges the importance, in terms of supporting the Committee’s work, of improved information-sharing between the Committee and the global coordination group under the global monitoring plan for persistent organic pollutants;

